--Uncomment the 4 lines below to create a stored procedure for data pipeline orchestrationâ€‹
--CREATE PROC bulk_load_dim_call_center
--AS
--BEGIN
COPY INTO tpcds.dim_call_center
(cc_call_center_sk 1, cc_call_center_id 2, cc_rec_start_date 3, cc_rec_end_date 4, 
cc_closed_date_sk 5, cc_open_date_sk 6, cc_name 7, cc_class 8, cc_employees 9, 
cc_sq_ft 10, cc_hours 11, cc_manager 12, cc_mkt_id 13, cc_mkt_class 14, 
cc_mkt_desc 15, cc_market_manager 16, cc_division 17, cc_division_name 18, cc_company 19, 
cc_company_name 20, cc_street_number 21, cc_street_name 22, cc_street_type 23, cc_suite_number 24, 
cc_city 25, cc_county 26, cc_state 27, cc_zip 28, cc_country 29, cc_gmt_offset 30, cc_tax_percentage 31)
FROM 'https://synapseintro002.dfs.core.windows.net/data/dwh-dataset/call_center.dat'
WITH
(
	FILE_TYPE = 'CSV'
	,MAXERRORS = 0
	,FIELDTERMINATOR = '|'
	,FIRSTROW = 1
	,ERRORFILE = 'https://synapseintro002.dfs.core.windows.net/_error_rows/'
)
--END
GO

SELECT TOP 100 * FROM tpcds.dim_call_center
GO
